VERSION 1
WHEN PRESENT (Environment\.getExternalStorageDirectory|Context\.getExternalFilesDir)\s*\(\)\s*.*\.(dex|so|jar|apk)
WHEN EXPR MISSING:verify|signature|checksum|MessageDigest && MISSING:test|example|sample
REPORT AS area_of_interest
REASON Detects storage of executable files on external storage.
TRACE Externalized rule logic for Executable File Storage on External Storage.
